interview_age.Description: Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging. | Age is rounded to chronological month. sex.Description: Sex of subject at birth | M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

eventname.Description: The event name for which the data was collected
